HCS SS#2 SB 1233 50
148 12. Nothing herein shall prohibit any director or
149 officer of a corporation, partner or a partnership, sole
150 proprietor of a business enterprise, member of a joint
151 venture, member of a committee appointed by stockholders,
152 creditors or courts, or an employee of any of the foregoing,
153 in his or her capacity as such, from signing, delivering or
154 issuing any financial, accounting or related statement, or
155 report thereon, relating to the corporation, partnership,
156 business enterprise, joint venture or committee, provided
