77 [(11)] (13) "Partnership", any partnership or limited
78 liability partnership;
79 [(12)] (14) "Person", any individual, corporation,
80 firm, partnership, association or other entity authorized to
81 do business;

HCS SS#2 SB 1233 55
82 [(13)] (15) "Professional engineer", any person
