20 required by this subdivision shall follow the completion of
21 the requirements of subdivisions (1) and (2) of this
22 section. This period of employment shall be under the
23 direct supervision of a [person who is licensed by the state
24 of Missouri in the profession in which the applicant seeks
25 to be] licensed speech-language pathologist in good standing
26 in any state. Persons applying with an audiology clinical
